{{!
    @template mod_englishcentral/mobile_no_iframe_embedding

    Message shown in the mobile app when iframe embedding is not
    enabled on the site, with a link to the relevant admin setting.

    Example context (json):
    {
    }
}}
<div style="padding: 1em">
    <div>Iframe embedding must be enabled in order to display Poodll EnglishCentral in the mobile app.</div>
    <div>You can enable it by checking "Allow frame embedding" in <a href="/admin/settings.php?section=httpsecurity">Site Administration / Security / Http Security</a></div>
</div>
